Here is the complete SCSS block for `.injections-section` including all nested selectors:

```scss
.injections-section {
	background-color: colors.$color-white;
	align-items: flex-start;
	padding: fonts.rem(64px);
	@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
		padding: fonts.rem(40px) 0;
	}

	// Left — gallery in .container
	.container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: fonts.rem(64px);
		@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: fonts.rem(24px);
		}
	}

	// Left — image gallery grid (desktop) + slider (tablet/mobile)
	.gallery-wrapper {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
			display: block;
			overflow: hidden;
			min-width: 0;
		}

		.gallery-carousel.grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
			grid-template-rows: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: fonts.rem(8px);
			@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
				display: none;
			}
		}

		.gallery-image {
			width: 100%;
			max-height: fonts.rem(462px);
			aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
			object-fit: cover;
			display: block;
		}

		// Slider + thumbnail nav (tablet/mobile only)
		.injections-slider-wrapper {
			display: none;
			@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
				display: block;
				overflow: hidden;
				min-width: 0;
			}

			.injections-main-carousel {
				position: relative;
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
				scrollbar-width: none;
				gap: fonts.rem(8px);
				margin-bottom: fonts.rem(12px);
				cursor: grab;
				@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
					padding-left: fonts.rem(32px);
					scroll-padding-left: fonts.rem(32px);
				}
				@media #{layout.$small-screen-only} {
					padding-left: fonts.rem(16px);
					scroll-padding-left: fonts.rem(16px);
				}

				&::-webkit-scrollbar {
					display: none;
				}

				&::after {
					content: '';
					flex-shrink: 0;
					width: max(#{fonts.rem(64px)}, calc(100vw - #{fonts.rem(462px)}));
					order: 9999;
				}

				.slide {
					scroll-snap-align: start;
					flex-shrink: 0;
					width: calc(100% - #{fonts.rem(32px)});
					max-width: fonts.rem(462px);
					@media #{layout.$small-screen-only} {
						width: calc(100% - #{fonts.rem(16px)});
					}

					&[data-slide="0"] {
						order: 1;
					}
					&[data-slide="1"] {
						order: 2;
					}
					&[data-slide="2"] {
						order: 4;
					}
					&[data-slide="3"] {
						order: 3;
					}
					&[data-slide="4"] {
						order: 5;
					}
					&[data-slide="5"] {
						order: 6;
					}
				}
			}

			.injections-thumbs {
				display: flex;
				gap: fonts.rem(8px);
				@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
					padding: 0 fonts.rem(32px);
				}
				@media #{layout.$small-screen-only} {
					padding: 0 fonts.rem(16px);
				}

				.thumb {
					flex: 1 1 0;
					min-width: 0;
					max-width: fonts.rem(54px);
					cursor: pointer;

					img {
						width: 100%;
						aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
						object-fit: cover;
						display: block;
						border-radius: fonts.rem(4px);
						border: 2px solid transparent;
						opacity: 0.5;
						transition: opacity 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
					}

					&.active img {
						opacity: 1;
						border-color: colors.$color-black;
					}
					&[data-slide="0"] {
						order: 1;
					}
					&[data-slide="1"] {
						order: 2;
					}
					&[data-slide="2"] {
						order: 4;
					}
					&[data-slide="3"] {
						order: 3;
					}
					&[data-slide="4"] {
						order: 5;
					}
					&[data-slide="5"] {
						order: 6;
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}

	// Right — content + FAQ
	.content-wrapper {
		flex: 1 0 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0;
		@media #{layout.$medium-screen-and-smaller} {
			flex: 0 0 auto;
			width: 100%;
